title: Prey Adaptation
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

If a unit containing a Malanthrope is involved in any close combat in which an enemy unit (or units) is destroyed, it may not perform a Sweeping Advance, but instead stops to feed on the dead. When it does so, from that Assault phase onwards, all friendly units within Synapse range of the Malanthrope gain the [[Preferred Enemy]] (all units from the same codex as the destroyed enemy unit(s)) for as long as thet remain within Synapse range of the Malanthrope.